text.section:
If the State Board has already issued a certificate of nomination for a nominee under this section, it promptly shall certify to the appropriate local boards:
the name and residence of the individual designated by the State central committee of the political party as the successor nominee to fill the vacancy;
the office for which the successor nominee is nominated;
the political party the successor nominee represents; and
the name of the individual for whom the successor nominee is substituted.
